<topic template="Default" lasteditedby="Georg Kiehne" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd" status="Needs Review">
  <title translate="true">Main toolbar</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Main toolbar</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:410px; margin-left:0px;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1" style="width:654px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:657px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="new_xform.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">New</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Depending on your settings, this entry either creates a blank flame or opens a window where you can select a basic flame style to start with.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="openHS.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true">  </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Open</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Opens a batch of your choice.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="saveHS.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true">  </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Save parameters</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Saves the currently selected flame into a batch of your choice.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="gear_1.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true">  </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Render to Disk</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Opens the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Rendering" styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">rendering</link><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> window for the currently selected flame.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="gear_2.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true">  </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Render All Flames</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Opens the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Rendering" styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">rendering</link><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> window for all flames in the currently open batch.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="LegendHS.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true">  </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">View Batch as List</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">If toggled on, the batch listing will not contain thumbnails.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="ThumbnailView.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true">  </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">View Batch as Icons</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">If toggled on, the batch listing will contain thumbnails.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="Edit_UndoHS.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Undo</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Reverts the recently made change within the currently selected flame.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="Edit_RedoHS.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Redo</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Re-applies the recently undone change within the currently selected flame.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="RestartHS.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Reset Location</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Resets the camera of the currently selected flame to its default location.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="FullScreenHS.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Full screen</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Displays the currently selected flame on the entire screen.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="FunctionHS.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Editor</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Opens the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Editor_window" styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">editor</link><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> window.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="EditTableHS.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Adjust</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Opens the camera tab of the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Adjustment" styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">adjustment</link><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> window.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="color.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Gradient</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Opens the gradient tab of the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Adjustment" styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">adjustment</link><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> window.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="ViewThumbnailsHS.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Mutation</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Opens the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Mutation" styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">mutation</link><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> window.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="CascadeWindowsHS.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Image size</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Opens the image size-tab of the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Adjustment" styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">adjustment</link><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> window.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="CheckGrammarHS.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Parser output</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Opens a window which shows all error messages generated by the last opened batch or selected flame.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="PropertiesHS.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Options</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Opens the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Options" styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">options</link><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> window.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="transparency.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Show transparency</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Toggles the visibility of flame transparency on or off. If toggled off, the selected background color of the flame will be shown as background.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="guides.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Show guide lines</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">If toggled on, the flame in the main preview will be overlayed with guide lines.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="EditCodeHS.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Edit Script</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Opens the script editor.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="PlayHS.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Run Script</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Runs the currently selected script.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="StopHS.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Stop Script</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Stops the currently running script.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="PointerHS.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Move mode</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">If toggled on, clicking and dragging in the main preview will move the camera.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="rotate.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Rotate mode</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">If toggled on, clicking and dragging in the main preview will rotate the camera.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="zoomin.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Zoom mode (zoom in)</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">If toggled on, clicking and dragging in the main preview will zoom the camera in.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><image src="zoomout.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Zoom mode (zoom out)</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;" translate="true">If toggled on, clicking and dragging in the main preview will zoom the camera out.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
</topic>
